{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"f1sy95vvl2cyfpto8miwxhh","title":"Styling","desc":"","updated":1687572263059,"created":1687489668726,"nav_order":3,"custom":{"nav_order":3},"fname":"web-components.styling","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"011ffb34c80d5fc777e8897504be0121","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"web-components.styling","id":"f1sy95vvl2cyfpto8miwxhh","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.styling.css-custom-properties","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":12,"offset":12},"end":{"line":2,"column":60,"offset":60},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.styling.css-custom-properties"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"web-components.styling","id":"f1sy95vvl2cyfpto8miwxhh","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.Apis.shadow-dom","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":63,"offset":63},"end":{"line":2,"column":97,"offset":97},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.Apis.shadow-dom"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"web-components.styling","id":"f1sy95vvl2cyfpto8miwxhh","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.styling.css-encapsulation","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":985},"end":{"line":26,"column":45,"offset":1029},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.styling.css-encapsulation"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"web-components.styling","id":"f1sy95vvl2cyfpto8miwxhh","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.styling.css-custom-properties","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1,"offset":1159},"end":{"line":29,"column":49,"offset":1207},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.styling.css-custom-properties"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"web-components.styling","id":"f1sy95vvl2cyfpto8miwxhh","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.styling.css-parts-api","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1,"offset":1454},"end":{"line":32,"column":41,"offset":1494},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.styling.css-parts-api"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"web-components.styling","id":"f1sy95vvl2cyfpto8miwxhh","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.styling.slotted-elements","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":76,"offset":1571},"end":{"line":34,"column":119,"offset":1614},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.styling.slotted-elements"}},{"from":{"fname":"web-components","id":"zkfccjgcs7b7pqvirwby57p","vaultName":"docs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":85,"offset":1536},"end":{"line":24,"column":119,"offset":1570},"indent":[]},"value":"web-components.styling"}],"anchors":{"estilos-globales":{"type":"header","text":"Estilos globales","value":"estilos-globales","line":11,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["5vihc22zv3ux3lduf3aaab6","fcj7t4u5hm6t7amh45uid1n","lgs19vv9v8nq2megefqyprn","3lzfo9vm01y09nvjbji1g25"],"parent":"zkfccjgcs7b7pqvirwby57p","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"styling\">Styling<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#styling\"></a></h1>\n<p>Utilizando <a href=\"/notes/5vihc22zv3ux3lduf3aaab6\">CSS Custom Properties</a> y <a href=\"/notes/efwvmwe8ctv925mkt5wrl5z\">shadow-dom</a> podemos crear temas y estilar nuestros componentes.</p>\n<h1 id=\"estilos-globales\">Estilos globales<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#estilos-globales\"></a></h1>\n<p> Uno de los puntos malos del CSS es que por default, el CSS es global. </p>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">h1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">red</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n</code></pre>\n<p> Esta regla hace que <strong>todos</strong> los <code>h1</code> sean rojos. Muchas veces solo queremos aplicar una regla a un componente o vista especifico. Para hacer esto en el pasado se utilizaban convenciones de nombres como BEM, para poder evitar que accidentalmente se pisaran estilos. Por ejemplo</p>\n<pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">h1<span class=\"token class\">.article-heading</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">blue</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">h1<span class=\"token class\">.article-heading</span> <span class=\"token class\">.article-heading--green</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">green</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n</code></pre>\n<p> De esta forma se evita que el estilo impacte en todos los h1 y solo en el que tiene la clase. Esto es mejor pero no es escalable ya que es posible que en proyectos grandes nos encontremos con colisiones en los nombres.</p>\n<p> Con Web Componenst podemos usar el Shadow DOM para simplificar como escribimos CSS.\n<a href=\"/notes/fcj7t4u5hm6t7amh45uid1n\">CSS Encapsulation</a></p>\n<p>Pero ¿Qué ocurre si queremos pisar los estilos del componente? Tal vez para usar un tema custom. Para esto nos van a servir las\n<a href=\"/notes/5vihc22zv3ux3lduf3aaab6\">CSS Custom Properties</a></p>\n<p>Mientras que las CSS Custom Properties permiten una mejor customización del componente y los temas, todavía puede haber veces en las que necesitemos más flexibilidad y debamos activar el estilo de elementos del DOM enteros en nuestro componente\n<a href=\"/notes/lgs19vv9v8nq2megefqyprn\">CSS Parts API</a></p>\n<p>Por ultimo nos queda ver como estilar componentes dentro de nuestros slots <a href=\"/notes/3lzfo9vm01y09nvjbji1g25\">Slotted Elements</a></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/fcj7t4u5hm6t7amh45uid1n\">CSS Encapsulation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/5vihc22zv3ux3lduf3aaab6\">CSS Custom Properties</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/lgs19vv9v8nq2megefqyprn\">CSS Parts API</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/3lzfo9vm01y09nvjbji1g25\">Slotted Elements</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/zkfccjgcs7b7pqvirwby57p\">Web Components</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1687572145233,"created":1687478467553,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"7b933c6af26999e634508c56679dd466","links":[{"type":"ref","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":155},"end":{"line":6,"column":20,"offset":174},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components"}}],"anchors":{"web-components-docs":{"type":"header","text":"Web Components DOCS","value":"web-components-docs","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["zkfccjgcs7b7pqvirwby57p"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n# Web Components DOCS\n\nEsta es una documentación de web components basada en el libro *Web Component Essentials* de Cory Rylan https://webcomponent.dev/\n\n![[web-components]]\n\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[